episodes.title: Investigation into the Legionaries of Christ- Part II
episodes.description: (Cheshire-WTNH, May 13, 2002 11:30 PM ) _ Tonight, a Team 8 investigation into charges of abuse by priests in a world wide Catholic, the Legion of Christ, order with a U.S. base right here in Connecticut. The Legionaries of Christ have a seminary in Cheshire.
